  "summary": "Malicious code in @spending-behavior-ui/widget-insights (npm)",
  "details": "Package @spending-behavior-ui/widget-insights@99.9.1 is a dependency-confusion attack. It ships an empty stub (module.exports = {}) and declares a dependency on \"ltidisafe\" resolved from an external URL at hxxps://ltidi[.]storage[.]googleapis[.]com/depenconf/ltidisafe-3[.]3[.]7[.]tgz. The high sentinel version (99.9.1) and scoped name mimicking an internal UI package are designed to win dependency resolution in npm install. The external tarball is the actual payload delivery mechanism.",
